#. <section class="sutta" id="sn31.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn31.4-12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 31"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 31"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn31.4-12:0.2"
msgid "1. Gandhabbavagga"
msgstr "1. Fairies"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4–​12. Sāragandhādidātāsuttanavaka → dātā 2--10 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn31.4-12:0.3"
msgid "4–​12. Sāragandhādidātāsuttanavaka"
msgstr "4–12. Nine Discourses On Givers of Fragrant Heartwood, etc."

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.252"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.3"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sāragandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why someone, when their body "
"breaks up, after death, is reborn in the company of the gods of fairykind "
"who live in fragrant heartwood …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.4"
msgid "pheggugandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "softwood …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.5"
msgid "tacagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "bark …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.6"
msgid "papaṭikagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "sprouts …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.7"
msgid "pattagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "leaves …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.8"
msgid "pupphagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "flowers …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.9"
msgid "phalagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "fruit …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.10"
msgid "rasagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr "sap …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.11"
msgid "gandhagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti?"
msgstr "fragrant scents?”"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.12"
msgid ""
"“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kāyena sucaritaṃ carati, vācāya sucaritaṃ carati, "
"manasā sucaritaṃ carati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicant, it’s when someone does good things by way of body, speech, and "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.13"
msgid "Tassa sutaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "And they’ve heard:"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.14"
msgid "‘sāragandhe adhivatthā devā dīghāyukā vaṇṇavanto sukhabahulā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The gods of fairykind who live in fragrant heartwood … fragrant scents are "
"long-lived, beautiful, and very happy.’"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.15"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.16"
msgid ""
"‘aho vatāhaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sāragandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ … "
"pe …"
msgstr ""
"‘If only, when my body breaks up, after death, I would be reborn in the "
"company of the gods of fairykind who live in fragrant heartwood …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.17"
msgid "pheggugandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.18"
msgid "tacagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.19"
msgid "papaṭikagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.20"
msgid "pattagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.21"
msgid "pupphagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.22"
msgid "phalagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.23"
msgid "rasagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.24"
msgid "gandhagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjeyyan’ti."
msgstr "fragrant scents!’"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.25"
msgid "So dātā hoti sāragandhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They give gifts of fragrant heartwood …"

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.26"
msgid "so dātā hoti pheggugandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.27"
msgid "so dātā hoti tacagandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.28"
msgid "so dātā hoti papaṭikagandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.29"
msgid "so dātā hoti pattagandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.30"
msgid "so dātā hoti pupphagandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.31"
msgid "so dātā hoti phalagandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.32"
msgid "so dātā hoti rasagandhānaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.33"
msgid "so dātā hoti gandhagandhānaṃ."
msgstr "fragrant scents."

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.34"
msgid ""
"So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā gandhagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the company of the "
"gods of fairykind who live in fragrant scents."

msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.35"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā gandhagandhe adhivatthānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why someone, when their body breaks "
"up, after death, is reborn in the company of the gods of fairykind who live "
"on fragrant scents.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn31.4-12:1.36"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
